05 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'05]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2007 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'07]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2008 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'08]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2009 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'09]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2010 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'10]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2011 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'11]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2012 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'12]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2013 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'13]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2014 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'14]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2015 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'15]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2017 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'17]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[2019 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'19]]\n|- align=center\n|  style=\"text-align:left; background:#e3e3e3;\"|'''Seeds\u2192'''||7||4||10||4||6||3||'''1'''*||9||4||4||'''1'''*||4||4||2||7\n|}\n<nowiki>*</nowiki> \u2013 Overall number one seed. The committee began ranking 1 seeds in 2004.\n\n===Complete NCAA Tournament results===\nThe Cardinals have appeared in the [[NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Championship|NCAA Tournament]] 39* (43) times. Their combined record is 61\u201344* (76\u201344).\n\n<nowiki>*</nowiki> \u2013 NCAA vacated all wins from 2011 to 2015.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Louisville Cardinals|Year|Seed|Round|Opponent|Result}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[1951 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|1951]] || || Sweet Sixteen || Kentucky || L 68\u201379\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[1959 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|1959]] || || First Round<br />Sweet Sixteen<br />Elite Eight<br />Final Four<br />National