on]]\n* [[2013 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|2013]] \u2013 [[Luke Hancock]]\n\n===NCAA Tournament seeding history===\n''The [[National Collegiate Athletic Association|NCAA]] began seeding the tournament with the [[1979 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|1979 edition]].''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|Years \u2192\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1979 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'79]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1980 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'80]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1981 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'81]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1982 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'82]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1983 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'83]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1984 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'84]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1986 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'86]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1988 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'88]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1989 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'89]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1990 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'90]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1992 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'92]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1993 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'93]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1994 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'94]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1995 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'95]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1996 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'96]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1997 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'97]]\n!style=\"background: #e3e3e3;\"|[[1999 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|'99]]\n|- align=center\n|  style=\"text-align:left; background:#e3e3e3;\"|'''Seeds\u2192'''||3||2||4||3||''