len Murphy]] || Guard/Forward || 1972\u201375\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|16 || [[Chuck Noble]] || Forward/Guard || 1950\u201354 \n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|13 || [[Bud Olsen]] || Center || 1959\u201362\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|15 || [[Jim Price (basketball)|Jim Price]] || Guard || 1969\u201372\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|13 || Kenny Reeves || Guard || 1946\u201350\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|9 || [[Phil Rollins]] || Guard || 1952\u201356\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|43 || [[Derek Smith (basketball)|Derek Smith]] || Guard/Forward || 1978\u201382\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|55 || [[Billy Thompson (basketball)|Billy Thompson]] || Forward  || 1982\u201386\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|22 || John Turner || Forward || 1958\u201361\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|20 || [[Milt Wagner]] || Guard || 1981\u201386\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|32 || [[DeJuan Wheat]] || Guard || 1993\u201397\n|}\n\n===Conference Player of the Year===\n\n====Key====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n| style=\"background:#cfecec;\"| \u2020\n|Co-Players of the Year\n|-\n|Player (X)\n|Denotes the number of times the player has been<br />awarded the Player of the Year award at that point\n|}\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:55%;\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Louisville Cardinals|border=0|color=white}};\"| [[Missouri Valley Conference Men's Basketball Player of the Year|{{color|white|Missouri Valley Conference Player of the Year}}]]\n|- align=center\n{{CollegeSecondaryHeader|team=Louisville Cardinals|Season|Player|Position|Class}}\n|- align=center\n| 1973\u201374\n| {{sortname|Junior|Bridgeman}}\n| [[Small forward|SF]]\n| {{sort|3|Junior}}\n|- align=center\n| 1974\u201375\n| {{sortname|Junior|Bridgeman}} (2)\n| [[Small forward|SF]]\n| {{sort|4|Senior}}\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Louisville Cardinals|borde